#

Spicy Shrimp Tacos

20 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

MexicanSeafood

Course:

Main CourseLunchDinner

Tags:

QuickEasySpicySeafood

Description

Deliciously spicy shrimp wrapped in soft tortillas, topped with fresh ingredients for a zesty kick!

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • chili powder: 1 tsp
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • garlic powder: 1/2 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • shredded cabbage: 1 cup
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime: 1, cut into wedges
